subSubSection.paragraph:
This species is very similar to
H. taehoani
sp. nov., but differs from the latter by having the POL 0.7 x Od (1.0-1.3 x in
H. taehoani
), hind femur wider, 3.6 x longer than wide (slender, 4.0-4.4 x longer than wide in
H. taehoani
), length of the first tergite 1.15 x its distal width (almost equal in
H. taehoani
) and second tergite entirely striate (striate only in the basal half in
H. taehoani
).
